Export Metadata to an Excel file

nmr_meta_export.Rd

Export Metadata to an Excel file

nmr_meta_export(
  nmr_dataset,
  xlsx_file,
  groups = c("info", "orig", "title", "external")
)

Arguments

nmr_dataset

An nmr_dataset_family object
xlsx_file

"The .xlsx excel file"
groups

A character vector. Use "external" for the external metadata or the default for a more generic solution

Value

The Excel file name
